ComicInfo.Summary:
Katchoo meets Lilith and discovers who is really behind the theft of Cleopatra's Papyrus. Meanwhile the kids set traps around the house to catch the "burglar" who has been watching the house.
Note: The digital edition (1/2/2019) for this issue was released before the print edition.
